Product - API(CRUD)
Backend -Node JS, Express, Mongo DB 

Modules/Packages: express,cors,morgan,dotenv,mongoose


npm init -y

npm i express cors morgan dotenv mongoose

DataBase Design 
================
Product Collection Schema

Collection/ Table - Product  
Field Name: Type

 name  : string,
 image : string,
 price : number , 
 qty   : number ,
 info  : string,
 created:Date 

REST API - CRUD 
1)Create a New Product/ Upload a New Product 
2)Read All Product
3)Read Product 
4)Update Product
5)Delelte Product 

1)Create a New Product 
URL:127.0.0.1:8080/api/newproduct
URL:127.0.0.1:8080/api/addproduct
Method:POST
Required Filed:name,image,price,qty,info

2)Read All Product
URL:127.0.0.1:8080/api/all
URL:127.0.0.1:8080/api/allProducts
Method:GET
Required Filed:None


Test API:
http://localhost:8080/
http://localhost:8080/api/allproduct
http://localhost:8080/api/delete/2
http://localhost:8080/api/edit/3
http://localhost:8080/api/all
